<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
  <title>Invalid QR — FoodToken</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: #f4f4f6;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 36px 28px;
      max-width: 360px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
    }
    .icon  { font-size: 52px; margin-bottom: 12px; display: block; }
    .title { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; color: #dc2626; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .body  { color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #9b2a2a;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 11px 28px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <span class="icon">❌</span>
    <h1 class="title">Invalid QR Code</h1>
    <p class="body">
      This QR code is invalid, has expired, or has been tampered with.<br>
      Please ask the employee to show a fresh token.
    </p>
    <a href="/" class="btn">Back to Home</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
